    {
      "id": "1924750c-f3ba-8005-9552-c89e5363287c",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Authors use instructional design to create SRL measures that are capturable from a LMS. Authors valdiate their approach on 2 distinct learning activities and compare how well their SRL measures actually map to SRL constructs obtainable from Self-Reports. Results show relatively high agreement between the authors methods’, but sometimes it does seem to generate a bias in the results. ",
      "raw": {
        "object": "block",
        "id": "1924750c-f3ba-8005-9552-c89e5363287c",
